msgstr "Ugrás az elejére"

#. Translators: Orca has a modal math navigation mode powered by MathCAT
#. (https://daisy.github.io/MathCAT). This command moves to the last item.
#: src/orca/cmdnames.py:1185
msgctxt "mathcat"
